org.deeplearning4j.models.embeddings.loader

Class WordVectorSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.models.embeddings.loader.WordVectorSerializer

  • public class WordVectorSerializer
extends Object
    This is utility class, providing various methods for WordVectors serialization List of available serialization methods (please keep this list consistent with source code):
    • Serializers for Word2Vec:
      • writeWordVectors(WeightLookupTable, File) writeWordVectors(WeightLookupTable, OutputStream) writeWord2VecModel(Word2Vec, File) writeWord2VecModel(Word2Vec, String) writeWord2VecModel(Word2Vec, OutputStream)
    • Deserializers for Word2Vec:
      • readWord2VecModel(File) readWord2VecModel(String) readWord2VecModel(File, boolean) readWord2VecModel(String, boolean) readAsBinaryNoLineBreaks(File) readAsBinary(File) readAsCsv(File) readBinaryModel(File, boolean, boolean) readWord2VecFromText(File, File, File, File, VectorsConfiguration) readWord2Vec(String, boolean) readWord2Vec(File, boolean) readWord2Vec(InputStream, boolean)
    • Serializers for ParaVec:
      • writeParagraphVectors(ParagraphVectors, File) writeParagraphVectors(ParagraphVectors, String) writeParagraphVectors(ParagraphVectors, OutputStream)
    • Deserializers for ParaVec:
      • readParagraphVectors(File) readParagraphVectors(String) readParagraphVectors(InputStream)
    • Serializers for GloVe:
      • writeWordVectors(Glove, File) writeWordVectors(Glove, String) writeWordVectors(Glove, OutputStream)
    • Adapters
      • fromTableAndVocab(WeightLookupTable, VocabCache) fromPair(Pair) loadTxt(File)
    • Serializers to tSNE format
      • writeTsneFormat(Glove, INDArray, File) writeTsneFormat(Word2Vec, INDArray, File)
    • FastText serializer:
      • writeWordVectors(FastText, File)
    • FastText deserializer:
      • readWordVectors(File)
    • SequenceVectors serializers:
      • writeSequenceVectors(SequenceVectors, OutputStream) writeSequenceVectors(SequenceVectors, SequenceElementFactory, File) writeSequenceVectors(SequenceVectors, SequenceElementFactory, String) writeSequenceVectors(SequenceVectors, SequenceElementFactory, OutputStream) writeLookupTable(WeightLookupTable, File) writeVocabCache(VocabCache, File) writeVocabCache(VocabCache, OutputStream)
    • SequenceVectors deserializers:
      • readSequenceVectors(File, boolean) readSequenceVectors(String, boolean) readSequenceVectors(SequenceElementFactory, File) readSequenceVectors(InputStream, boolean) readSequenceVectors(SequenceElementFactory, InputStream) readLookupTable(File) readLookupTable(InputStream)
    Author:
    Adam Gibson, raver119, alexander@skymind.io

        Parameters:
        stream - InputStream that contains previously serialized model
        skipFirstLine - Set this TRUE if first line contains csv header, FALSE otherwise
        Returns:
        Throws:
        IOException

      • loadStaticModel

        public static WordVectors loadStaticModel(InputStream inputStream)
                                   throws IOException
        This method restores previously saved w2v model. File can be in one of the following formats: 1) Binary model, either compressed or not. Like well-known Google Model 2) Popular CSV word2vec text format 3) DL4j compressed format In return you get StaticWord2Vec model, which might be used as lookup table only in multi-gpu environment.
        Parameters:
        inputStream - InputStream should point to previously saved w2v model
        Returns:
        Throws:
        IOException
